These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
City: boston, miami
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, boat
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, vegafina
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, jazz
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, green
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, dahlia
2 different games are played: whist, snooker
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who likes green##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
5. the person playing snooker is the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the fan of jazz is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| City      | miami        | boston |
| Transport          | boat  | bike     |
| Cigar         | vegafina    | montecristo         |
| Music-Genre           | indie    | jazz |
| Color   | mauve  | green     |
| Flower           | dahlia      | poppy    |
| Game         | snooker | whist          |

