2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
