2. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
3. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
4. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
